WEBVTT

00:03:56.112 --> 00:04:00.300
the organizers delivered hundreds of eggs
to various government buildings

00:04:00.324 --> 00:04:01.491
with a message:

00:04:01.960 --> 00:04:03.846
"If you don't have the huevos" --

00:04:03.870 --> 00:04:05.076
the balls --

00:04:05.100 --> 00:04:08.154
"to stop corrupt candidates
from running for office,

00:04:08.178 --> 00:04:09.636
you can borrow ours."

00:04:09.660 --> 00:04:11.319
(Laughter)

00:04:11.343 --> 00:04:14.698
(Applause)

00:04:16.469 --> 00:04:17.988
President Molina responded

00:04:18.012 --> 00:04:20.148
by vowing that he would never step down.

00:04:20.674 --> 00:04:24.275
And the activists realized
that they couldn't just keep protesting

00:04:24.299 --> 00:04:26.313
and ask the president to resign.

00:04:26.337 --> 00:04:28.333
They needed to leave him no choice.

00:04:28.793 --> 00:04:30.724
So they organized a general strike,